statement: theorem ψe7lρiθhtψeΓφ5ℕP (x y : dBNaΤ) (h : ΚμD x y = oΜℕe) : x = oΜℕe := by
proof:

    -- Case x = ΙMτr leads to contradiction since ΚμD ΙMτr y = ΙMτr ≠ oΜℕe

      apply MQΧBoeωnρΥcc

        apply Ih9ℂυMrKℕBσcΓneΗ _ _ (lBut n)
        rw [ℂCs_ℝΥψd]
        apply ycqbigHj
        exact h'
      rw [this]
      rfl
